{"tid":1384762,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"「不合作運動魚蛋論」我無得返工你都要冇得返","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:05:49.000Z","uid":81236,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcbe875c96b116e3632f2fe0710dcc0f62f5368","tid":1384762,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"首先，不合作運動既源頭係政府！佢既先係始作俑者。<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動既然已經事在必行，咁多位打工仔有冇諗過點解人地有得返工，我地冇得返？<br />\n<br />\n點解高官有私家車可以返工？點解行馬路既車可以返工？公平咩？<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要令對方都冇得返！<br />\n<br />\n塞車無罪，堵路有理！"},{"pid":"1f3be64c878f1a14e9ca32e09fe8d5a9a5806f6a","tid":1384762,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:00:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9b464205ee9ca22fdac004e91bc1ecfe5e6b9c47","tid":1384762,"uid":115977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:02:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5日大罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6e1ce150c4c80732e490735a6040889f152aa30c","tid":1384762,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e58b10e6e8c3013c868713f789bcb2bf01f45c8","tid":1384762,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}